<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-67-0642 </DOCNO><TEXT>Coal is going to remain the prime source of energy for years to come andthe consumption will rise with time. The railways are already overburdenedand to reduce their load coal slurry transportation through pipelinesis the most suitable alternative. Preparation of right type of slurryneeds controlled size reduction of run of mine coal. A technical discussionof various factors associated with the mechanism of comminution, advantages,various equipment and their combination, have been attempted in thispaper. 10 refs., 5 figs., 1 tab.</TEXT></DOC>